trans-unit.source: Contains information about an area of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Contiene informazioni relative a un'area del controllo <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar" />.
Questa classe non può essere ereditata.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitTestInfo> objects are returned by <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar> controls in response to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitTest%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitTestInfo> gli oggetti sono restituiti da <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar> controlli in risposta al <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitTest%2A> metodo.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitTestInfo> is for informational purposes only; you should not construct these objects and cannot modify any of the members.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitTestInfo> solo a scopo informativo è non devono costruire questi oggetti e non è possibile modificare uno dei membri.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitArea" /> that represents the area of the calendar evaluated by the hit-test operation.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene l'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitArea" /> che rappresenta l'area del calendario valutata dall'operazione di verifica.

trans-unit.source: Gets the point that was hit-tested.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene il punto che è stato sottoposto a verifica.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Point" /> containing the <see cref="P:System.Drawing.Point.X" /> and <see cref="P:System.Drawing.Point.Y" /> values tested.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Point" /> contenente i valori <see cref="P:System.Drawing.Point.X" /> e <see cref="P:System.Drawing.Point.Y" /> sottoposti a verifica.

trans-unit.source: Gets the time information specific to the location that was hit-tested.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene le informazioni sull'ora specifiche per la posizione sottoposta a verifica.

trans-unit.source: The time information specific to the location that was hit-tested.
trans-unit.target: Informazioni sull'ora specifiche alla posizione sottoposta a verifica.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitTestInfo.Time%2A> property contains a valid date when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitArea> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitArea.Date> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitArea.WeekNumbers>.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitTestInfo.Time%2A> proprietà contiene un valore valido di date quando il <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitArea> è impostata su <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitArea.Date> o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar.HitArea.WeekNumbers>.
